## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-102">声明是有关颁发者通过主题的语句。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-102">A claim is a statement about a subject by an issuer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-103">声明表示属性的使用者的身份验证和授权操作的上下文中有用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-103">Claims represent attributes of the subject that are useful in the context of authentication and authorization operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-104">使用者和颁发者是这两个实体的标识方案的一部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-104">Subjects and issuers are both entities that are part of an identity scenario.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-105">使用者的一些典型示例包括： 用户、 应用程序或服务、 设备或计算机。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-105">Some typical examples of a subject are: a user, an application or service, a device, or a computer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-106">颁发者的一些典型示例包括： 操作系统、 应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-106">Some typical examples of an issuer are: the operating system, an application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-107">是服务、 角色提供程序、 标识提供程序或联合身份验证提供程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-107">a service, a role provider, an identity provider, or a federation provider.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-108">颁发者颁发安全令牌，通常通过安全令牌服务 (STS)，以提供声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-108">An issuer delivers claims by issuing security tokens, typically through a Security Token Service (STS).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-109">(在 WIF，您可以通过派生自生成 STS<xref:System.IdentityModel.SecurityTokenService>类。)有时，可以通过直接在资源上存储的使用者属性扩展收到来自颁发者声明的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-109">(In WIF, you can build an STS by deriving from the <xref:System.IdentityModel.SecurityTokenService> class.) On occasion, the collection of claims received from an issuer can be extended by subject attributes stored directly at the resource.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-110">声明可以评估以确定对数据访问权限以及其他的授权过程中保护的资源和也可以使用或 express 关于某主题的身份验证决策。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-110">A claim can be evaluated to determine access rights to data and other secured resources during the process of authorization and can also be used to make or express authentication decisions about a subject.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-111">从.NET 4.5 开始，Windows Identity Foundation (WIF) 类，实现基于声明的标识，该已完全集成到.NET Framework。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-111">Beginning with .NET 4.5, the Windows Identity Foundation (WIF) classes, which implement claims-based identity, have been fully integrated into the .NET Framework.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-112">由实现声明概念<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-112">The claims concept is implemented by the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-113">下面介绍的重要属性<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim>类：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-113">The following describes important properties of the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim> class:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-114"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A>属性是一个字符串 (通常是一个 URI) 包含有关声明的语义信息; 它告诉了声明的值的含义。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-114">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A> property is a string (typically a URI) that contains the semantic information about the claim; it tells you what the value of the claim means.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-115">例如，具有声明类型的声明<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes.GivenName>("http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2005/05/identity/claims/givenname") 表示用户的名字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-115">For example, a claim with a claim type of <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes.GivenName> ("http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2005/05/identity/claims/givenname") represents a user’s first name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-116">值<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A>属性可以是中定义的已知声明类型之一<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes>类，也可以是任意一个 URI，定义的颁发者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-116">The value of the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A> property can be one of the well-known claim types defined in the <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes> class, or it can be an arbitrary URI as defined by the issuer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-117">例如，"urn: spendinglimit"的声明类型可以表示该颁发者的业务上下文中有意义的用户属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-117">For example, a claim type of "urn:spendinglimit" might represent a user attribute which makes sense within the business context of the issuer.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-118"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A>属性包含的声明的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-118">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A> property contains the value of the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-119">为了减少依赖关系并简化管理，可在 WIF 声明的值被表示仅为字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-119">In order to reduce dependencies and simplify administration, in WIF the value of a claim is represented only as a string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-120">对于更复杂的值类型，建议使用标准的 XML 架构类型来指示如何序列化到本应，从字符串反序列化值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-120">For more complex value types, it is recommended that you use standard XML schema types to indicate how the value is meant to be serialized into and deserialized from a string.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-121"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A>属性包含一个字符串，标识值的类型信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-121">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A> property contains a string that identifies the type information for the value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-122">若要了解值的格式并提供有关如何进行反序列化的信息，应使用此属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-122">This property should be used to understand the format of the value and to provide information about how to deserialize it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-123">如果解决方案需要复杂值类型，建议使用中的标准 XML 架构类型<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A>属性以指示如何<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A>本应将序列化到，从字符串反序列化属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-123">If your solution requires complex value types, it is recommended that you use standard XML schema types in the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A> property to indicate how the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A> property is meant to be serialized into and deserialized from a string.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-124"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Subject%2A>属性是<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity>表示声明主题的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-124">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Subject%2A> property is a <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity> object that represents the subject of the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-125">声明主题是有关添加声明的实体 （通常请求的用户是对资源的访问）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-125">The subject of the claim is the entity (typically the user who is requesting access to a resource) about which the claim is asserted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-126"><xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity>包含，其属性之间的描述属性的声明集合和属性的使用者，因为一个或多个颁发者证明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-126">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity> contains, among its properties, a collection of claims that describe the properties and attributes of the subject as attested to by one or more issuers.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-127"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A>属性包含颁发声明的实体的名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-127">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A> property contains the name of the entity that issued the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-128">颁发者的声明由包含来自已知颁发者颁发者名称注册表维护列表的名称的字符串表示在 WIF 中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-128">The issuer of a claim is represented in WIF by a string that contains a name taken from a list of well-known issuers that is maintained by the issuer name registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-129">颁发者名称注册表是派生的类的实例<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.IssuerNameRegistry>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-129">The issuer name registry is an instance of a class that derives from the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.IssuerNameRegistry> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-130">颁发者名称注册表将验证由相应发行人生成的标志签名所需的加密材料的助记键名称相关联。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-130">The issuer name registry associates a mnemonic name to the cryptographic material needed to verify the signatures of tokens produced by the corresponding issuer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-131">例如，<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry>类，可立即与.NET 4.5 中，将每个颁发者的助记键名称与及其相应的 X.509 证书相关联。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-131">For example, the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry> class, available out of the box with .NET 4.5, associates the mnemonic name for each issuer with its corresponding X.509 certificate.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-132">已知颁发者的列表通常在启动时生成的颁发者名称注册表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-132">The list of well-known issuers is typically built at startup time by the issuer name registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-133">使用列表<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry>应用程序配置文件中指定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-133">The list used by the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry> is specified in the application configuration file.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-134"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A>属性包含最初发出声明的实体的名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-134">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A> property contains the name of the entity that originally issued the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-135">此属性则设计的方案，其中一个声明可能通过多个颁发者显示客户端向信赖方应用程序;例如联合身份验证的情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-135">This property is designed to facilitate scenarios where a claim may pass through multiple issuers before it is presented by the client to the RP application; such as federation scenarios.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-136">你可以检查<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A>属性来确定最初发出声明的实体。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-136">You can examine the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A> property to determine the entity that originally issued the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-137">该名称被从列表中的已知颁发者颁发者名称注册表中，如下所示的大小写由维护<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-137">The name is taken from the list of well-known issuers maintained by the issuer name registry, as in the case of the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-138">下面的示例提取关联到执行 HTTP 请求的经过身份验证用户的声明，并将其写入 HTTP 响应中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-138">The following example extracts the claims associated to the authenticated user performing an HTTP request and writes them in the HTTP response.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-139">当前用户读取<xref:System.Web.HttpContext>作为<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsPrincipal>和从其读取声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-139">The current user is read from the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> as a <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsPrincipal> and the claims are read from it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee2d9-140">声明对写入<xref:System.Web.HttpResponse>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee2d9-140">The claims are then written to the <xref:System.Web.HttpResponse> object.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
ClaimsPrincipal principal = HttpContext.Current.User as ClaimsPrincipal;  
if (null != principal)  
{  
   foreach (Claim claim in principal.Claims)  
   {  
      Response.Write("CLAIM TYPE: " + claim.Type + "; CLAIM VALUE: " + claim.Value + "</br>");  
   }  
  
}  
  
```
